{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>KIDDO</strong> is a point-and-click adventure game packed with clever puzzles, a striking hand-drawn art style, and an ironic sense of humor... because if you\u2019re going to hit rock bottom, you might as well do it with style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story follows Kiddo, a socially isolated person who has truly mastered the art of doing nothing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time has slipped through your fingers, and you\u2019re still there\u2014glued to your sofa, watching life slip away like the last slice of pizza at a party you weren\u2019t invited to. Your motivation? Gone. Your friends? Ghosted. Your job? Let\u2019s not even go there. Even your house is giving up on itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But hey, it\u2019s not all bad. There\u2019s still one person who believes in you. Well\u2026 kinda.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you muster the strength to get up and turn things around? Or at least shower? Are you ready to give life another shot?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Come on, Kiddo. It\u2019s time. (No, really. Your sofa is starting to smell.)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THIS GAME IS FOR YOU IF:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2714 You\u2019re bored. Like, staring-at-the-ceiling bored. <br>\u2714 You enjoy puzzles that make you question your intelligence. <br>\u2714 You appreciate a good story with just the right amount of existential crisis. <br>\u2714 You love hand-drawn art because pixels are <i>so</i> mainstream. <br>\u2714 You, too, have found yourself in &quot;the dark hole&quot; (no, not your laundry pile).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This Demo is the first Episode of 3.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sof\u00e1 Samurai","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3533310/597a35741373526565598084b68d31d93c3f6a24.jpg"},{"name":"Enviromental activist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/p